description:
LORA made by lykon
https://civitai.com/models/5477/lucy-cyberpunk-edgerunners-lora
If you really want Lucy, I highly recommend going for the LORA.

Embedding for Lucy from edgerunners. You probably already noticed but deep danbooru doesn't have data for characters after 2020 so you'll have a hard time recreating characters after that time period if you're relying on their danbooru tags.

It's a gamble whether or not you'll get those weird white short flaps she has on her thighs. Trying to make a V3 version and see if I can make it anymore consistent because I love it.

2 versions:
lucy_kushinada trained on 28 images for 3000 steps.
- rougher, more close to anime line work.
- I think
- requires more keywords to get the outfit together

lucy_kushinadaV2 trained on 178 images for 5000 steps.
- I'll upload all the steps version for this as well
- more consistent outfit, less keywords needed

mess around with the strength values if you want to see different variations.
Example :
(lucy_kushinadaV2:0.8)

All models are based on FusionDance and anything Vae
https://civitai.com/models/3958/fusiondanceanime

X/Y plot of the different iterations, honestly can't tell the difference up to you guys to see and experiment.

https://imgur.com/a/iWEsr6z

*NOTE
Beautiful feet/toes are not guaranteed in this embbeding. I personally spent hours sculpting every toe on this Goddesses' feet.

Please step on me.
